---
// Cohort marker (immovable) vs Genesis NFT (tradeable)
---
<figure class="adm-diagram" aria-label="Cohort marker versus Genesis NFT">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 860 260" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-labelledby="cm-title cm-desc">
    <title id="cm-title">Cohort marker versus Genesis NFT</title>
    <desc id="cm-desc">The cohort marker is permanently bound to the original validator address. The Genesis NFT is freely tradeable. They are separate artefacts.</desc>
    <style>
      .d-text { font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif; }
      .d-mono { font-family: "Geist Mono", "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; }
      .d-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; opacity: 0.6; }
    </style>

    <!-- left: marker -->
    <rect x="20" y="40" width="400" height="200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
    <text x="40" y="78"  class="d-mono d-eyebrow" fill="currentColor">IMMOVABLE</text>
    <text x="40" y="116" class="d-text" font-size="26" fill="currentColor">Cohort marker</text>
    <text x="40" y="146" class="d-text" font-size="14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7">attached to the original address</text>
    <text x="40" y="166" class="d-text" font-size="14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7">for the lifetime of the chain</text>

    <!-- lock motif -->
    <g transform="translate(320,80) scale(2.2)">
      <rect x="0" y="10" width="30" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"/>
      <path d="M 6 10 V 5 a 9 9 0 0 1 18 0 V 10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"/>
      <circle cx="15" cy="21" r="2.4" fill="currentColor"/>
    </g>

    <!-- right: NFT -->
    <rect x="460" y="40" width="380" height="200" fill="var(--paper-3)" stroke="currentColor"/>
    <text x="480" y="78"  class="d-mono d-eyebrow" fill="currentColor">TRADEABLE</text>
    <text x="480" y="116" class="d-text" font-size="26" fill="currentColor">Genesis NFT</text>
    <text x="480" y="146" class="d-text" font-size="14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7">no protocol function</text>
    <text x="480" y="166" class="d-text" font-size="14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7">cultural artefact · transferable</text>

    <!-- exchange motif -->
    <g transform="translate(740,110)" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5">
      <path d="M 0 8 L 50 8 L 40 -2 M 50 8 L 40 18"/>
      <path d="M 50 36 L 0 36 L 10 26 M 0 36 L 10 46"/>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="adm-diagram-caption">Two artefacts, one cohort · WP §8.1.9</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .adm-diagram { margin: 24px 0; border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); }
  .adm-diagram svg { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  .adm-diagram > svg { padding: 24px; }
  .adm-diagram-caption { border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); padding: 10px 18px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: 0.10em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-3); background: var(--paper-2); }
</style>
